    "lines": [
      "# Continuous Verification Model",
      "",
      "Zero trust, or 零信任, replaces network-based trust with continuous identity and device checks.",
      "",
      "## Model",
      "",
      "持续验证模型重新评估主体、设备和资源风险，而不是永久授予会话信任。",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "Perimeterless security and never trust always verify are related labels. 无边界安全是对应中文说法。",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "Policy evaluation needs fresh telemetry and an explicit least-privilege fallback."
    ],
